    "Evaluation": {
      "text": "Confirm by serology\nCulture\nHypokalemia\n/\nHyponatremia\nThrombocytopenia\nUA\nwith sterile pyuria\nElevated CK\nCSF\nwith elevated wbcs and protein with normal glucose",
