    "Management": {
      "text": "Penicillin G\n100000U/ kg/ dose IV every 6 hours x 7days\nOR\n>8yrs:\nDoxycycline\n4mg/kg/dose oral every 12 hours x 7 days\n<8yrs:\nAmpicillin\n75-100mg/kg/dose oral every 6 hours x 7days\n<8yrs:\nAmoxicillin\n50mg/kg/dose oral 6- 8 hours x 7days\nOther alternatives:\nCeftriaxone\n,\nCefotaxime\n[5]\nPrefer\nAzithromycin\nor\nDoxycycline\nif unable to distinguish from rickettsial infection.\nBe aware of the potential for a\nJarisch-Herxheimer Reaction",
